OL,3,CLabour could beat Reform in general
OL,4,Celection if led by Andy Burnham, polls
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FA Labour Party with Andy Burnham at
OL,8,Fthe helm could beat Reform UK in a
OL,9,Fgeneral election, a poll suggests.
OL,11,FThe More in Common survey found that
OL,12,Fif a general election was held
OL,13,Ftomorrow, Labour would get an eight
OL,14,Fpoint boost with Mr Burnham as leader,
OL,15,Fsecuring 30% of the vote to Reform's
OL,16,F27%.
OL,18,FThe Conservatives would trail on 20%,
OL,19,Fthe Liberal Democrats on 11% and the
OL,20,FGreen Party on 7%.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
