OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1779307555
OL,3,CLabour could beat Reform in general
OL,4,Celection if led by Andy Burnham, polls
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FMr Burnham is seeking to return to
OL,8,FWestminster via the upcoming
OL,9,FMakerfield by-election and potentially
OL,10,Fchallenge Sir Keir for the keys to No
OL,11,F10.
OL,13,FAs Labour leader, Mr Burnham would win
OL,14,Fback a third of voters who have
OL,15,Fditched the party since the 2024
OL,16,Fgeneral election, according to More in
OL,17,FCommon's survey of 2,599 Britons.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
