CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1779307555
OL,3,CLabour could beat Reform in general
OL,4,Celection if led by Andy Burnham, polls
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FNearly half of defectors to the Greens
OL,8,For Lib Dems would return to Labour, as
OL,9,Fwell as a fifth of those who have
OL,10,Fmoved rightwards to Reform or the
OL,11,FTories.
OL,13,FMr Burnham's leadership would dent the
OL,14,FGreen Party's momentum under Zack
OL,15,FPolanski, with its support dropping
OL,16,Ffrom 11% to 7% in a hypothetical
OL,17,Felection.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
