OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1779307555
OL,3,CLabour could beat Reform in general
OL,4,Celection if led by Andy Burnham, polls
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FMore in Common UK director Luke Tryl
OL,8,Fsaid: "This is one of the most high-
OL,9,Fstakes by-elections in history, and
OL,10,Fthe future trajectory of the Labour
OL,11,FParty, and indeed British politics
OL,12,Fmore broadly, may depend on what
OL,13,Fhappens in the next month.
OL,15,F"So far, it looks like Andy Burnham's
OL,16,Fappeal extends beyond Greater
OL,17,FManchester.
OL,26,@pD@GOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
