OL,3,CLabour could beat Reform in general
OL,4,Celection if led by Andy Burnham, polls
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,F"In a hypothetical general election,
OL,8,Fhe could give Labour a lead over
OL,9,FReform ` winning back progressive
OL,10,Fvoters who have drifted away, but also
OL,11,Fmaking gains with some of those the
OL,12,Fparty has lost to Reform.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
