OL,3,CLabour could beat Reform in general
OL,4,Celection if led by Andy Burnham, polls
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,F"That said, people recognise the
OL,8,Fmayorlty and premiership are different
OL,9,Froles and a large part of Burnham's
OL,10,Fappeal rests on championing the north
OL,11,Fand fighting Westminster ` if he is
OL,12,Fsuccessful in Makerfield, it could be
OL,13,Fchallenging to sustain his reputation
OL,14,Fas an outsider from within the House
OL,15,Fof Commons, especially during this era
OL,16,Fof anti-politics."
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@RO]
