OL,3,CLabour could beat Reform in general
OL,4,Celection if led by Andy Burnham, polls
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FAnd most ` 81% ` believed being prime
OL,8,Fminister was a difficult job, compared
OL,9,Fto just over half saying the Greater
OL,10,FManchester mayor role was tough.
OL,12,FAsked to describe Mr Burnham in a
OL,13,Fsingle word, the most common responses
OL,14,Fwere "ambitious", "good", and
OL,15,F"hopeful", while more negative ones
OL,16,Fincluded "opportunist" and "arrogant".
