OL,3,CLabour could beat Reform in general
OL,4,Celection if led by Andy Burnham, polls
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FMr Burnham has been confirmed as
OL,8,FLabour's candidate in the Makerfield
OL,9,Fby-election, which was triggered by
OL,10,Fformer minister Josh Simons quitting
OL,11,Fto open up a path for his to return to
OL,12,Fthe Commons.
OL,14,FAlong with Andy Burnham, the other
OL,15,Fdeclared candidates hoping to win the
OL,16,Fseat are:
OL,18,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,19,Four political experts are across all
OL,20,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,21,Fto the latest episode below...
